{"surah":{"number":63,"name":"المنافقون","englishName":"Al-Munafiqun","englishTranslation":"The Hypocrites","ayahCount":11},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:25.038Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"When the hypocrites come to you, [O Muhammad], they say, \"We testify that you are the Messenger of Allah.\" And Allah knows that you are His Messenger, and Allah testifies that the hypocrites are liars.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِذَا","english":"When","translit":"idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"جَآءَكَ","english":"come to you","translit":"jāaka","root":"جيأ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْمُنَـٰفِقُونَ","english":"the hypocrites","translit":"l-munāfiqūna","root":"نفق"},{"position":4,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","english":"they say","translit":"qālū","root":"قول"},{"position":5,"arabic":"نَشْهَدُ","english":"We testify","translit":"nashhadu","root":"شهد"},{"position":6,"arabic":"إِنَّكَ","english":"that you","translit":"innaka","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"لَرَسُولُ","english":"(are) surely (the) Messenger","translit":"larasūlu","root":"رسل"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ ۗ","english":"(of) Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","english":"And Allah","translit":"wal-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/063_001_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"يَعْلَمُ","english":"knows","translit":"yaʿlamu","root":"علم","audio":"wbw/063_001_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"إِنَّكَ","english":"that you","translit":"innaka","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_001_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"لَرَسُولُهُۥ","english":"(are) surely His Messenger","translit":"larasūluhu","root":"رسل","audio":"wbw/063_001_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","english":"and Allah","translit":"wal-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/063_001_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"يَشْهَدُ","english":"testifies","translit":"yashhadu","root":"شهد","audio":"wbw/063_001_015.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"that","translit":"inna","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_001_016.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"ٱلْمُنَـٰفِقِينَ","english":"the hypocrites","translit":"l-munāfiqīna","root":"نفق","audio":"wbw/063_001_017.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"لَكَـٰذِبُونَ","english":"(are) surely liars","translit":"lakādhibūna","root":"كذب","audio":"wbw/063_001_018.mp3"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"They have taken their oaths as a cover, so they averted [people] from the way of Allah. Indeed, it was evil that they were doing.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱتَّخَذُوٓا۟","english":"They take","translit":"ittakhadhū","root":"أخذ"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَيْمَـٰنَهُمْ","english":"their oaths","translit":"aymānahum","root":"يمن"},{"position":3,"arabic":"جُنَّةًۭ","english":"(as) a cover","translit":"junnatan","root":"جنن"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَصَدُّوا۟","english":"so they turn away","translit":"faṣaddū","root":"صدد"},{"position":5,"arabic":"عَن","english":"from","translit":"ʿan","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"سَبِيلِ","english":"(the) Way","translit":"sabīli","root":"سبل"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ ۚ","english":"(of) Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":8,"arabic":"إِنَّهُمْ","english":"Indeed, [they]","translit":"innahum","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_002_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"سَآءَ","english":"evil is","translit":"sāa","root":"سوأ","audio":"wbw/063_002_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_002_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"كَانُوا۟","english":"they used to","translit":"kānū","root":"كون","audio":"wbw/063_002_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"يَعْمَلُونَ","english":"do","translit":"yaʿmalūna","root":"عمل","audio":"wbw/063_002_013.mp3"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"That is because they believed, and then they disbelieved; so their hearts were sealed over, and they do not understand.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"That","translit":"dhālika","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"بِأَنَّهُمْ","english":"(is) because","translit":"bi-annahum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","english":"they believed","translit":"āmanū","root":"أمن"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","english":"then","translit":"thumma","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","english":"they disbelieved","translit":"kafarū","root":"كفر"},{"position":6,"arabic":"فَطُبِعَ","english":"so were sealed","translit":"faṭubiʿa","root":"طبع"},{"position":7,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"[upon]","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"قُلُوبِهِمْ","english":"their hearts","translit":"qulūbihim","root":"قلب"},{"position":9,"arabic":"فَهُمْ","english":"so they","translit":"fahum","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"لَا","english":"(do) not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":11,"arabic":"يَفْقَهُونَ","english":"understand","translit":"yafqahūna","root":"فقه"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"And when you see them, their forms please you, and if they speak, you listen to their speech. [They are] as if they were pieces of wood propped up - they think that every shout is against them. They are the enemy, so beware of them. May Allah destroy them; how are they deluded?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"۞ وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_004_002.mp3"},{"position":2,"arabic":"رَأَيْتَهُمْ","english":"you see them","translit":"ra-aytahum","root":"رأي","audio":"wbw/063_004_003.mp3"},{"position":3,"arabic":"تُعْجِبُكَ","english":"pleases you","translit":"tuʿ'jibuka","root":"عجب","audio":"wbw/063_004_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَجْسَامُهُمْ ۖ","english":"their bodies","translit":"ajsāmuhum","root":"جسم","audio":"wbw/063_004_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَإِن","english":"and if","translit":"wa-in","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_004_007.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"يَقُولُوا۟","english":"they speak","translit":"yaqūlū","root":"قول","audio":"wbw/063_004_008.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"تَسْمَعْ","english":"you listen","translit":"tasmaʿ","root":"سمع","audio":"wbw/063_004_009.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"لِقَوْلِهِمْ ۖ","english":"to their speech","translit":"liqawlihim","root":"قول","audio":"wbw/063_004_010.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"كَأَنَّهُمْ","english":"as if they (were)","translit":"ka-annahum","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_004_012.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"خُشُبٌۭ","english":"pieces of wood","translit":"khushubun","root":"خشب","audio":"wbw/063_004_013.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"مُّسَنَّدَةٌۭ ۖ","english":"propped up","translit":"musannadatun","root":"سند","audio":"wbw/063_004_014.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"يَحْسَبُونَ","english":"They think","translit":"yaḥsabūna","root":"حسب","audio":"wbw/063_004_016.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"كُلَّ","english":"every","translit":"kulla","root":"كلل","audio":"wbw/063_004_017.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"صَيْحَةٍ","english":"shout","translit":"ṣayḥatin","root":"صيح","audio":"wbw/063_004_018.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمْ ۚ","english":"(is) against them","translit":"ʿalayhim","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_004_019.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"هُمُ","english":"They","translit":"humu","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_004_021.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"ٱلْعَدُوُّ","english":"(are) the enemy","translit":"l-ʿaduwu","root":"عدو","audio":"wbw/063_004_022.mp3"},{"position":18,"arabic":"فَٱحْذَرْهُمْ ۚ","english":"so beware of them","translit":"fa-iḥ'dharhum","root":"حذر","audio":"wbw/063_004_023.mp3"},{"position":19,"arabic":"قَـٰتَلَهُمُ","english":"May destroy them","translit":"qātalahumu","root":"قتل","audio":"wbw/063_004_025.mp3"},{"position":20,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ ۖ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/063_004_026.mp3"},{"position":21,"arabic":"أَنَّىٰ","english":"How","translit":"annā","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_004_028.mp3"},{"position":22,"arabic":"يُؤْفَكُونَ","english":"are they deluded","translit":"yu'fakūna","root":"أفك","audio":"wbw/063_004_029.mp3"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"And when it is said to them, \"Come, the Messenger of Allah will ask forgiveness for you,\" they turn their heads aside and you see them evading while they are arrogant.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"قِيلَ","english":"it is said","translit":"qīla","root":"قول"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","english":"to them","translit":"lahum","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"تَعَالَوْا۟","english":"Come","translit":"taʿālaw","root":"علو"},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَسْتَغْفِرْ","english":"will ask forgiveness","translit":"yastaghfir","root":"غفر"},{"position":6,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","english":"for you","translit":"lakum","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"رَسُولُ","english":"(the) Messenger","translit":"rasūlu","root":"رسل"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"(of) Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":9,"arabic":"لَوَّوْا۟","english":"They turn aside","translit":"lawwaw","root":"لوي"},{"position":10,"arabic":"رُءُوسَهُمْ","english":"their heads","translit":"ruūsahum","root":"رأس"},{"position":11,"arabic":"وَرَأَيْتَهُمْ","english":"and you see them","translit":"wara-aytahum","root":"رأي"},{"position":12,"arabic":"يَصُدُّونَ","english":"turning away","translit":"yaṣuddūna","root":"صدد"},{"position":13,"arabic":"وَهُم","english":"while they","translit":"wahum","root":""},{"position":14,"arabic":"مُّسْتَكْبِرُونَ","english":"(are) arrogant","translit":"mus'takbirūna","root":"كبر"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"It is all the same for them whether you ask forgiveness for them or do not ask forgiveness for them; never will Allah forgive them. Indeed, Allah does not guide the defiantly disobedient people.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"سَوَآءٌ","english":"(It) is same","translit":"sawāon","root":"سوي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمْ","english":"for them","translit":"ʿalayhim","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَسْتَغْفَرْتَ","english":"whether you ask forgiveness","translit":"astaghfarta","root":"غفر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","english":"for them","translit":"lahum","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَمْ","english":"or","translit":"am","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"لَمْ","english":"(do) not","translit":"lam","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"تَسْتَغْفِرْ","english":"ask forgiveness","translit":"tastaghfir","root":"غفر"},{"position":8,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","english":"for them","translit":"lahum","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"لَن","english":"Never","translit":"lan","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"يَغْفِرَ","english":"will forgive","translit":"yaghfira","root":"غفر"},{"position":11,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله"},{"position":12,"arabic":"لَهُمْ ۚ","english":"[to] them","translit":"lahum","root":""},{"position":13,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_006_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/063_006_015.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"لَا","english":"(does) not","translit":"lā","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_006_016.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"يَهْدِى","english":"guide","translit":"yahdī","root":"هدي","audio":"wbw/063_006_017.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"ٱلْقَوْمَ","english":"the people","translit":"l-qawma","root":"قوم","audio":"wbw/063_006_018.mp3"},{"position":18,"arabic":"ٱلْفَـٰسِقِينَ","english":"the defiantly disobedient","translit":"l-fāsiqīna","root":"فسق","audio":"wbw/063_006_019.mp3"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"They are the ones who say, \"Do not spend on those who are with the Messenger of Allah until they disband.\" And to Allah belongs the depositories of the heavens and the earth, but the hypocrites do not understand.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"هُمُ","english":"They","translit":"humu","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"(are) those who","translit":"alladhīna","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"يَقُولُونَ","english":"say","translit":"yaqūlūna","root":"قول"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَا","english":"(Do) not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"تُنفِقُوا۟","english":"spend","translit":"tunfiqū","root":"نفق"},{"position":6,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"on","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"مَنْ","english":"(those) who","translit":"man","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"عِندَ","english":"(are) with","translit":"ʿinda","root":"عند"},{"position":9,"arabic":"رَسُولِ","english":"(the) Messenger","translit":"rasūli","root":"رسل"},{"position":10,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"(of) Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":11,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰ","english":"until","translit":"ḥattā","root":""},{"position":12,"arabic":"يَنفَضُّوا۟ ۗ","english":"they disband","translit":"yanfaḍḍū","root":"فضض"},{"position":13,"arabic":"وَلِلَّهِ","english":"And for Allah","translit":"walillahi","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/063_007_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"خَزَآئِنُ","english":"(are the) treasures","translit":"khazāinu","root":"خزن","audio":"wbw/063_007_015.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","english":"(of) the heavens","translit":"l-samāwāti","root":"سمو","audio":"wbw/063_007_016.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ","english":"and the earth","translit":"wal-arḍi","root":"أرض","audio":"wbw/063_007_017.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"وَلَـٰكِنَّ","english":"but","translit":"walākinna","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_007_018.mp3"},{"position":18,"arabic":"ٱلْمُنَـٰفِقِينَ","english":"the hypocrites","translit":"l-munāfiqīna","root":"نفق","audio":"wbw/063_007_019.mp3"},{"position":19,"arabic":"لَا","english":"(do) not","translit":"lā","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_007_020.mp3"},{"position":20,"arabic":"يَفْقَهُونَ","english":"understand","translit":"yafqahūna","root":"فقه","audio":"wbw/063_007_021.mp3"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"They say, \"If we return to al-Madinah, the more honored [for power] will surely expel therefrom the more humble.\" And to Allah belongs [all] honor, and to His Messenger, and to the believers, but the hypocrites do not know.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَقُولُونَ","english":"They say","translit":"yaqūlūna","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَئِن","english":"If","translit":"la-in","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَّجَعْنَآ","english":"we return","translit":"rajaʿnā","root":"رجع"},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِلَى","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْمَدِينَةِ","english":"Al-Madinah","translit":"l-madīnati","root":"مدن"},{"position":6,"arabic":"لَيُخْرِجَنَّ","english":"surely, will expel","translit":"layukh'rijanna","root":"خرج"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْأَعَزُّ","english":"the more honorable","translit":"l-aʿazu","root":"عزز"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مِنْهَا","english":"from it","translit":"min'hā","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْأَذَلَّ ۚ","english":"the more humble","translit":"l-adhala","root":"ذلل"},{"position":10,"arabic":"وَلِلَّهِ","english":"But for Allah","translit":"walillahi","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/063_008_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْعِزَّةُ","english":"(is) the honor","translit":"l-ʿizatu","root":"عزز","audio":"wbw/063_008_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"وَلِرَسُولِهِۦ","english":"and for His Messenger","translit":"walirasūlihi","root":"رسل","audio":"wbw/063_008_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"وَلِلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","english":"and for the believers","translit":"walil'mu'minīna","root":"أمن","audio":"wbw/063_008_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"وَلَـٰكِنَّ","english":"but","translit":"walākinna","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_008_015.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"ٱلْمُنَـٰفِقِينَ","english":"the hypocrites","translit":"l-munāfiqīna","root":"نفق","audio":"wbw/063_008_016.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"لَا","english":"(do) not","translit":"lā","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_008_017.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"يَعْلَمُونَ","english":"know","translit":"yaʿlamūna","root":"علم","audio":"wbw/063_008_018.mp3"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"O you who have believed, let not your wealth and your children divert you from remembrance of Allah. And whoever does that - then those are the losers.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","english":"O","translit":"yāayyuhā","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"you (who)","translit":"alladhīna","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","english":"believe","translit":"āmanū","root":"أمن"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَا","english":"(Let) not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"تُلْهِكُمْ","english":"divert you","translit":"tul'hikum","root":"لهو"},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَمْوَٰلُكُمْ","english":"your wealth","translit":"amwālukum","root":"مول"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَلَآ","english":"and not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"أَوْلَـٰدُكُمْ","english":"your children","translit":"awlādukum","root":"ولد"},{"position":9,"arabic":"عَن","english":"from","translit":"ʿan","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"ذِكْرِ","english":"(the) remembrance","translit":"dhik'ri","root":"ذكر"},{"position":11,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ ۚ","english":"(of) Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":12,"arabic":"وَمَن","english":"And whoever","translit":"waman","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_009_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"يَفْعَلْ","english":"does","translit":"yafʿal","root":"فعل","audio":"wbw/063_009_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"that","translit":"dhālika","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_009_015.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"فَأُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ","english":"then those","translit":"fa-ulāika","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_009_016.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"هُمُ","english":"[they]","translit":"humu","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_009_017.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"ٱلْخَـٰسِرُونَ","english":"(are) the losers","translit":"l-khāsirūna","root":"خسر","audio":"wbw/063_009_018.mp3"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"And spend [in the way of Allah] from what We have provided you before death approaches one of you and he says, \"My Lord, if only You would delay me for a brief term so I would give charity and be among the righteous.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَنفِقُوا۟","english":"And spend","translit":"wa-anfiqū","root":"نفق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَّا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"رَزَقْنَـٰكُم","english":"We have provided you","translit":"razaqnākum","root":"رزق"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"قَبْلِ","english":"before","translit":"qabli","root":"قبل"},{"position":7,"arabic":"أَن","english":"[that]","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"يَأْتِىَ","english":"comes","translit":"yatiya","root":"أتي"},{"position":9,"arabic":"أَحَدَكُمُ","english":"(to) one of you","translit":"aḥadakumu","root":"أحد"},{"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْمَوْتُ","english":"the death","translit":"l-mawtu","root":"موت"},{"position":11,"arabic":"فَيَقُولَ","english":"and he says","translit":"fayaqūla","root":"قول"},{"position":12,"arabic":"رَبِّ","english":"My Lord","translit":"rabbi","root":"ربب"},{"position":13,"arabic":"لَوْلَآ","english":"Why not","translit":"lawlā","root":""},{"position":14,"arabic":"أَخَّرْتَنِىٓ","english":"You delay me","translit":"akhartanī","root":"أخر"},{"position":15,"arabic":"إِلَىٰٓ","english":"for","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":16,"arabic":"أَجَلٍۢ","english":"a term","translit":"ajalin","root":"أجل"},{"position":17,"arabic":"قَرِيبٍۢ","english":"near","translit":"qarībin","root":"قرب"},{"position":18,"arabic":"فَأَصَّدَّقَ","english":"so I would give charity","translit":"fa-aṣṣaddaqa","root":"صدق"},{"position":19,"arabic":"وَأَكُن","english":"and be","translit":"wa-akun","root":"كون"},{"position":20,"arabic":"مِّنَ","english":"among","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":21,"arabic":"ٱلصَّـٰلِحِينَ","english":"the righteous","translit":"l-ṣāliḥīna","root":"صلح"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"But never will Allah delay a soul when its time has come. And Allah is Acquainted with what you do.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَن","english":"But never","translit":"walan","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يُؤَخِّرَ","english":"will (be) delayed","translit":"yu-akhira","root":"أخر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"(by) Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله"},{"position":4,"arabic":"نَفْسًا","english":"a soul","translit":"nafsan","root":"نفس"},{"position":5,"arabic":"إِذَا","english":"when","translit":"idhā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"جَآءَ","english":"has come","translit":"jāa","root":"جيأ"},{"position":7,"arabic":"أَجَلُهَا ۚ","english":"its term","translit":"ajaluhā","root":"أجل"},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","english":"And Allah","translit":"wal-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/063_011_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"خَبِيرٌۢ","english":"(is) All-Aware","translit":"khabīrun","root":"خبر","audio":"wbw/063_011_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"بِمَا","english":"of what","translit":"bimā","root":"","audio":"wbw/063_011_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"تَعْمَلُونَ","english":"you do","translit":"taʿmalūna","root":"عمل","audio":"wbw/063_011_012.mp3"}]}]}
